creator: Teenage Fashion Dress Up
descriptionHtml:
Do makeover for highschool fashionistas: pick makeup and facial features, shirts, jackets, coats, skirts, pants, hats, hairstyles and accessories. Style cute students without any locks or in-app purchases: all our fashion games are totally free. Just download and play on your Android phone or tablet!

Try that geeky look of a college student with nerdy glasses, brackets and a bunch of intelligent math text books :) Or instead create some popular fashionista image with a prom queen title and a career of a podium supermodel ahead. Or maybe come up with more amazing outfits and looks in this virtual doll salon application. To you as an outfit designer and a beauty expert, only your imagination is the limit. Hide the GUI with the "camera" button, grab a screenshot and share it on your social profile to show off your talents and skills to your classmates.

If you're really into cosplay and makeovers, press "More games" button to check out our new trendy dressup and styling apps.

descriptionShort: Dress up and make up 2 girl friends. 400+ items of clothing in cool girl games!
title: High School BFFs: Girls Team

creator: Teenage Fashion Dress Up
descriptionHtml:
If you really like dressing up teen girl games, this one is surely for you. Help high school popular girls to get an ideal dress up makeover. These BFF fashionistas have a cool college life, full of parties and fun. They know that being the most stylish is not that easy, but they have a lot of awesome clothes.

In our free dress up games for girls you can choose makeup, hairstyle and any clothes you want: shirts, jackets, skirts, hats and so on. High school uniform is not necessarily a boring thing, your college students’ outfits can be amazing and interesting. So style cute BFF in teenage fashion games and find an ideal look.

Try all the sides of a college life dressing up: a geeky look with nerdy glasses and brackets or a popular fashionista image with a prom queen clothing and a career of a podium supermodel ahead. Or come up with more amazing outfits in these it girl dress up games for teens. You are a fashion designer and style expert for college students, the only limit is your imagination!

💖 Enjoy FANTASTIC dressup makeover: 💖
🌸 2 pretty dolls on the screen at once to create BFF matching looks
🌸 A lot of types of clothes from skirts to gloves
🌸 Fashionable accessories and haircuts for dressing up
🌸 Awesome dress up games for teenage girls offline
🌸 Bright backgrounds of a college life
🌸 Ability to take a screenshot and show off your talent

Choose makeup (for eyes, lips and cheeks) & high school clothes you want – nice shirts, unusual tunics, bright sneakers and ripped jeans. There are 400+ items of clothing of teenage style! Any cool it girl will find something stylish for herself in our dress up games free offline.

After the makeover you can choose a background – canteen, hallway, street, library, sports hall or a class room. Whether it’s a lesson of math or library, your clothing should be perfect. Nice fashion college girls are really keen on dressing up & being the best of the best and their outfits and makeup speak for themselves.

You can add glasses, piercing and stickers to create the most fascinating BFF look in these cool it girl games for free. The only rule in this high school is being stylish, so don’t be afraid of wearing red and green bright clothes and mix everything as you want. Dress up, make up and have fun!

All the college students need books, phone, laptop, gloves and bags to bring all these things. You can add such accessories and much more in our dressing up teen girl games. Take a screenshot and share it to show off your fashion talents and style skills to your classmates.

If you're really into cosplay and makeover for a high school girl squad, press "More Games" button to check out our new trendy college dressup and styling apps. Choose clothes for cool BFF fashionistas in our outfit games and unleash your talents!
